## Ubuntu 20.4.6 LTS 安装Freqtrade
> 新建用户来安装conda

```bash
useradd freqtrade
passwd freqtrade
su freqtrade
wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
chmod 777 Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
./Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
```
> 安装完后参照：
https://www.freqtrade.io/en/stable/installation/#installation-with-conda

```bash
# download freqtrade
git clone https://github.com/freqtrade/freqtrade.git

# enter downloaded directory 'freqtrade'
cd freqtrade
conda create --name freqtrade python=3.12

    Do you accept the Terms of Service (ToS) for https://repo.anaconda.com/pkgs/main? [(a)ccept/(r)eject/(v)iew]: a
    Do you accept the Terms of Service (ToS) for https://repo.anaconda.com/pkgs/r? [(a)ccept/(r)eject/(v)iew]: a
    Preparing transaction: done
    Verifying transaction: done
    Executing transaction: done
    #
    # To activate this environment, use
    #
    #     $ conda activate freqtrade
    #
    # To deactivate an active environment, use
    #
    #     $ conda deactivate


```
> 进入 conda freqtrade

```bash
(base) r720@r720-PowerEdge-R720:~/freqtrade_local/freqtrade$ conda activate freqtrade
(freqtrade) r720@r720-PowerEdge-R720:~/freqtrade_local/freqtrade$

```
> 使用pip安装最后一个python依赖项

```bash
python3 -m pip install --upgrade pip
python3 -m pip install -r requirements.txt
python3 -m pip install -e .
```
> 关于conda的命令

```bash
# 查看当前conda的所有生成的应用项目
conda env list

# 激活基本的conda环境
conda activate

# 激活 freqtrade 激活基本的conda环境
conda activate freqtrade

#退出当前的conda环境
conda deactivate
```
